Invocation Name: westmoreland county scanner
des:
This is a live audio feed of public safety from Westmoreland County. 
 The skill is made with the Broadcastify stream which is a volunteer effort. 
 You may hear moments of siolence after the add plays. The stream is working though. This is live. Everything you hear is delayed by about 60 seconds. 
 This stream is on an as is bases.
 Just ask Alexa, Launch Westmoreland Scanner, an ad will play and the stream will begin. 
 
 Have questions? Comments? Concerns? Send those to TimothyClarkMusic@me.com 







 Made with Love in Jesus Name.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
